{"tid":1025704,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"做左一首新歌，阿李 X 甲乙丙戊 - 青春","createTime":"2019-02-17T13:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T16:34:56.000Z","uid":164192,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ce30c9d6ac30c40a9f0d84ed97ae3616ca85f708","tid":1025704,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"送俾大家最新製作嘅單曲 - 青春<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CYd7HLVZoFI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCYd7HLVZoFI&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=bd329335\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CYd7HLVZoFI</a><br />\n自從製作完個伴奏，就不斷改個編曲，一直到錄音/混音，期間都係不斷去修改唔同嘅位置，好希望可以製造到心目中想營造嘅氛圍。<br />\n首先好多謝 甲乙丙戊 願意 幫首歌Featuring，加左佢嘅人聲，令到歌曲更加有層次，而且我好鍾意佢嘅歌聲，雖然好多人都話聲線似阿 Kay，但係細心聽，甲乙丙戊就係甲乙丙戊，有佢獨特嘅質感，獨一無二嘅音色。🙏<br />\n另外好多謝 Ricky Pro 幫副歌填詞，我自己好鍾意當中嘅意思，首歌我係先搵佢填左詞，之後有感而發，先開始寫自己想表達嘅 Rap。<br />\n好多謝以上兩位朋友。🙏<br />\nI hope you will love the song. Many thanks."},{"pid":"b0f71695559f86c3ba4ad2b0228f115ba8dd0726","tid":1025704,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"🙏"},{"pid":"d3f637b4389b8e5770a3fe5e212ad3ee4aac27f5","tid":1025704,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74110af65cd65b2e1632aae8b198f3c23a02c36","tid":1025704,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T19:13:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5cef69c6f47d2b1632c35f664f772e0806de9ec3","tid":1025704,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3f637b4389b8e5770a3fe5e212ad3ee4aac27f5","tid":1025704,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"多謝！"},{"pid":"554fe14ff89164e91cadd0b38190bb9a82e2371a